"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?18/57/19346?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Nausea and vomiting with cancer treatment (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?2/39/2676?source=see_link\">",
